lead_paragraph: DREADEUL ACCIDENT.--A young man from the the neighborhood of Terre Haute, Named J.H. Cannon, we believe, who had come to this city with a drove of horses, fell out of the third story window of Mr. Linn's tavern night before last. The injuries received from the fall caused his death yesterday morning.
